Àtụ:Infobox badminton player
Eneojo Joseph Abah (amuru 16 February 1990) bu onye egwu badminton nke Naijiria
Abah si Kogi State, North Central Nigeria
A họpụtara ya ka ọ nọchite anya Naijiria na asọmpi mba ụwa n'afọ 2005 na asọmpi Junior nke Africa na Etiopia
Na 2010, ọ gbara asọmpi na Commonwealth Games na New Delhi, India
